The evidence with the title 'The state pension shakeup that could leave you with nothing at all ' says Mar 7, 2016  ... Under the current system people are entitled to some state pension  ... They worked part-time or for low pay – would get about £19.30 a week.  ... Set to lose out are 50,000 women and 20,000 men in their 50s and 60s, according to Age UK.  ... To obtain the full rate you will need to have made at least 35 years' ... 
